high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk over to the side of the coffee table that the couch is on.
Pick up the remote off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the chair, then turn right and walk to the chair with the credit card on its seat.
Put the remote on the seat of the chair to the left of the credit card.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right again and walk over to the table that the television is on.
Pick up the leftmost remote off of the table in front of you.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the chair with the remote and credit card on its seat.
Put the remote on the seat of the chair to the left of the remote that is already there.
